[div class=p 
	"Clockwork Cat is a classic flash game made for Ludum Dare 27, with the theme "10 seconds". You only have a limited amount of time to complete each section of the level before you run out of time.
	$LF
]div
[pre 
	$LF
]pre
[h3 id=GameObjectives 
	" Game objectives
	$LF
]h3
[ul 
	[li 
		" Emulator used: libTAS 1.4.4 + Ruffle Nightly 2023-08-28
		$LF
